256
00:12:40.570 --> 00:12:44.240
On the left, I am the Left Baskerville!

257
00:12:44.990 --> 00:12:49.210
On the right, I am the Right Baskerville!

258
00:12:49.210 --> 00:12:52.250
And in the center, it is I,

259
00:12:52.250 --> 00:12:54.130
Central Freeway!

260
00:12:54.130 --> 00:12:55.340
– Say what?!
– Say what?!

261
00:12:55.710 --> 00:12:57.550
Ch-Chief Justice!

262
00:12:57.550 --> 00:13:00.970
A pirate is going on a rampage
on the main island,

263
00:13:00.970 --> 00:13:04.600
but the men are saying they can't
get in touch with Chief Spandam.

264
00:13:04.600 --> 00:13:05.930
Please assume command!

265
00:13:06.310 --> 00:13:09.440
A pirate, you say. Pirates are guilty!

266
00:13:12.100 --> 00:13:15.820
Oh, come on. Let him off with a warning.

267
00:13:17.530 --> 00:13:19.490
Then, let's compromise and give him...

268
00:13:19.490 --> 00:13:20.820
the death penalty!

269
00:13:20.820 --> 00:13:22.200
– Say what?!
– Say what?!

270
00:13:24.370 --> 00:13:26.580
There's trouble, Chief Justice!

271
00:13:26.580 --> 00:13:30.960
We got a report that Straw Hat's comrades
took out Kashi at the island gate...

272
00:13:30.960 --> 00:13:32.960
and that Oimo is losing too!

273
00:13:32.960 --> 00:13:35.750
– What?! Don't let them breach the gate!
– What?! Don't let them breach the gate!

274
00:13:37.250 --> 00:13:40.970
– Send 100 watchdogs immediately!
– Send 100 watchdogs immediately!

275
00:13:40.970 --> 00:13:42.090
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

276
00:13:46.310 --> 00:13:49.350
Dammit! The five minutes are over!

277
00:13:46.350 --> 00:13:49.350
<b>Island Gate
Enies Lobby</b>

278
00:13:49.350 --> 00:13:53.020
This is bad! Hurry up
and clear the path for Rocketman!

279
00:13:53.020 --> 00:13:55.480
You aren't passing through this gate!

280
00:13:57.320 --> 00:13:59.070
We got the gate unlocked!

281
00:13:59.070 --> 00:14:01.150
Now we gotta push open the doors!

282
00:14:01.150 --> 00:14:02.780
What?! Ah, crud!

283
00:14:02.780 --> 00:14:04.030
Alright! Good going!

284
00:14:04.030 --> 00:14:05.780
Go!

285
00:14:06.450 --> 00:14:09.080
No one's touching this gate!

286
00:14:09.500 --> 00:14:11.250
Rope Action...

287
00:14:12.250 --> 00:14:14.170
Top Knot!

288
00:14:14.170 --> 00:14:15.580
Take this!

289
00:14:17.540 --> 00:14:20.510
Whoa! That's a Galley-La foreman, alright!

290
00:14:20.510 --> 00:14:23.630
What?! This puny rope...

291
00:14:24.470 --> 00:14:26.680
Franky Family! Pull!

292
00:14:26.680 --> 00:14:27.930
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

293
00:14:28.810 --> 00:14:32.180
Just leave it to us! Let's go,
Sodom and Gomorrah! Grab the rope!

294
00:14:40.030 --> 00:14:42.530
Charge into the gate!

295
00:14:43.570 --> 00:14:47.280
H-Hey! Hold on! Oimo's feeling dizzy!

296
00:14:47.280 --> 00:14:49.490
Push the doors!

297
00:14:55.250 --> 00:14:56.880
Look! The doors...!

298
00:14:56.880 --> 00:14:58.170
The doors are opening!

299
00:14:58.790 --> 00:15:00.590
What happened to Oimo?!

300
00:15:01.090 --> 00:15:02.550
